## API Services

This software integrates with the following third-party API services:

### Google Gemini AI
- **Terms of Service**: https://ai.google.dev/terms
- **Privacy Policy**: https://policies.google.com/privacy
- Users must obtain their own API key and agree to Google's terms of service

### Indian Kanoon API
- **Terms of Service**: https://api.indiankanoon.org/
- Users must obtain their own API token and comply with Indian Kanoon's usage policies

### Court Listener API
- **Terms of Service**: https://www.courtlistener.com/terms/
- **Privacy Policy**: https://www.courtlistener.com/privacy/
- Users must obtain their own API token and comply with Court Listener's terms

