## Data Privacy

- This software processes data locally in the user's browser
- API calls to third-party services (Google Gemini AI, Indian Kanoon, Court Listener) are subject to those services' privacy policies
- Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.) when using this software
- No user data is collected or stored by the NyayaAssist project maintainers

